CPD-TGW3D-8a

CPD-TGW3D-8a.jl is a Julia library to perform topological gift arrangement on cellular complexes expressed through the Linear Algebraic Representation (LAR). This library is developed by Scarano, Malvati, Di Lorenzo as a project for the Calcolo Parallelo e Distribuito exam.

Dependencies

CPD-TGW3D-8a.jl has several Julia dependencies:

  • LinearAlgebraicRepresentation
  • BenchmarkTools
  • ViewerGL
